@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Create form with default content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Student Course Feedback"
}

### Create form with custom content
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Employee Satisfaction Survey",
  "content": "{\"title\":\"Custom Survey\",\"questions\":[{\"id\":1,\"text\":\"Satisfaction?\",\"type\":\"single_choice\",\"required\":true,\"options\":[\"Satisfied\",\"Neutral\",\"Dissatisfied\"]}]}"
}

### List all forms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forms

### Get form by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forms/1

### Generate public link for form
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms/1/public-link

### Regenerate public link
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms/1/public-link

### Create form without title - expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "missing title"
}

### Get non-existent form - expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forms/999

### Generate link for non-existent form - expect 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/forms/999/public-link
